criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 20 and ≤59 years ;

          -  Healthy volunteers;

          -  Written informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Ferro-magnetic prosthesis, aneurysm clips, severe claustrophobia or other
             contraindications or exclusions interfering with the MRI assessment;

          -  Pregnancy (due to safety reasons).
